# File:         clipb
# Description:  Clipboard managers warper that SuperB
# Author:       NNB
#               └─ https://github.com/NNBnh
# URL:          https://github.com/NNBnh/clipb
# License:      GPLv3

#    This program is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify
